The '''Jesa Corporation''' was a [[Mining/Legends|mining]] operation which was established and operated by individuals of high moral character. They helped turn the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Pergitor]] into a lucrative and popular world, though despite their good intentions, Jesa's continued mining eventually led to an increase in [[Volcano/Legends|volcanic]] activity, causing the world to become uninhabitable.

